    "description": "Randoville 是一款中世纪城市建设游戏，但却有一个<strong>转折</strong>。<br>你的一举一动都将受到 <strong>D20</strong> 立方体的控制！<br><br>[list］<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>建筑外观<br></li><li>资源点的质量<br></li><li>提取的资源数量<br></li><li>事件结果[/list］将由投掷 D20 决定！<br>不过别灰心，运气是可以改善的！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/1a9e361cbd8f81a8a08ae9c13b29f4c6.poster.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/1a9e361cbd8f81a8a08ae9c13b29f4c6.webm?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/1a9e361cbd8f81a8a08ae9c13b29f4c6.mp4?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/13b4eb0d53bd2bf6127ee7721fff2a0e.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>选择要建造的建筑，掷骰子并得出结果！<br>数字越大，你就越容易建造。<br>建造、赚钱、提升等级并打开新世界。<br>一旦陷入困境，就放弃一切，重新开始！<br>完美是没有极限的，所以你可以随心所欲地重头再来，孜孜不倦的小崽子们会帮助你达到巅峰！<br>尽量不要用你的巨型骰子伤害它们！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/7c83592b337e47aef1a1d4d6fe782ceb.poster.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/7c83592b337e47aef1a1d4d6fe782ceb.webm?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/7c83592b337e47aef1a1d4d6fe782ceb.mp4?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/6b6c765efabac995143bd437b3caa48a.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>如果你厌倦了做一名中世纪建筑师，不妨试试钓鱼，或者......我不知道，矿山卡丁车赛车联盟？这些小游戏会让你忘却烦恼，并为你的村庄赚取一些有用的东西。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/a243caf38dd9a33568a9353e90773300.poster.avif?t=1698686664\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/a243caf38dd9a33568a9353e90773300.webm?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2357310/extras/a243caf38dd9a33568a9353e90773300.mp4?t=1698686664\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></li></ul>",
